{"tid":47824,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"「求救」賣左車，但買家唔轉名","createTime":"2016-12-20T15:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T10:46:22.000Z","uid":32246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88a60cd67b2f5a21c8b9df6fe55e698f747791d1","tid":47824,"uid":32246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"家人十二月頭賣左架車，當時買家話無帶身分證正本。而要後補轉名，果時無為意。<br />\n<br />\n但直到近日收到告票先發現一直無轉名，而又聯絡唔到買家。<br />\n<br />\n去警署，又話未轉名唔應該俾車人（我都知有問題做錯左），就叫我地去運輸署。無講可以點做，仲叫我地自己去搵果個買家（就係搵唔到）<br />\n<br />\n想知道依家可以做啲咩，因為架車應該過左期仲未驗車，但佢仲周圍揸緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17bc56c0194a3b93aabe1f0ac840c6f73add248","tid":47824,"uid":40179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"報失先"},{"pid":"419d206bd54fee7b064a5586f522cf78c7cd7710","tid":47824,"uid":61929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"報警話失車"},{"pid":"2915cb8332cb37031db615ed05cb78aefb75d316","tid":47824,"uid":47023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未轉名就咪撚交部車俾人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e0b76e12467a790470457ea47f8d281f011b2c","tid":47824,"uid":32246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警話失車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我家人去警署備案已經話左成個詳情俾佢，但警方唔肯做野，再報失會唔會受理？"},{"pid":"939c84453b62cf6183507a6ec887e24e52267102","tid":47824,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報警話失車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我家人去警署備案已經話左成個詳情俾佢，但警方唔肯做野，再報失會唔會受理？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你收左錢賣俾人 仲可以報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c33939f127e15fad43400428343faffc9d281a","tid":47824,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報警話失車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我家人去警署備案已經話左成個詳情俾佢，但警方唔肯做野，再報失會唔會受理？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你收左錢賣俾人 仲可以報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然名義上架車係你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114922bd8160170cc775e24a98afaaf58e2fe382","tid":47824,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"手續都未搞完當然可以報失"},{"pid":"3752a7d2d3a67f5f46e6e7aa6b10ba0958a3bea9","tid":47824,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"車仲係你名下係唔係俾人偷咗"},{"pid":"e41bd48468d461237f95589f3d7b2751e3d48889","tid":47824,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我家人去警署備案已經話左成個詳情俾佢，但警方唔肯做野，再報失會唔會受理？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你收左錢賣俾人 仲可以報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然名義上架車係你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話冇收過錢得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7a6df39f04f63e05a6e0e9db9e874ef3562c29","tid":47824,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你收左錢賣俾人 仲可以報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然名義上架車係你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話冇收過錢得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n需要講大話？<br />\n名義上架車唔係仲你你架咩？"},{"pid":"571